## ⚙️ GitHub Actions Setup (CI)
In `.github/workflows/lint.yml`:
```yaml
name: Lint Code Base
on: [push]
jobs:
  lint:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v3
      - name: Set up Python
        uses: actions/setup-python@v4
        with:
          python-version: '3.x'
      - name: Install flake8
        run: pip install flake8
      - name: Run flake8
        run: flake8 .
```

